        "# Hypothesis Testing : Bombay Hospitality Ltd."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "Muh_SDIKGJGt"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## Step 1: Problem Background & Hypotheses\n",
        "### Background:\n",
        "##### Bombay Hospitality Ltd. uses the cost model:\n",
        "##### W = 1000 + 5X\n",
        "##### where X is the number of units produced in a week.\n",
        "##### Restaurant owners claim the actual operating costs are higher.\n",
        "\n",
        "### Hypotheses:\n",
        "##### H0: μ = 1000 + 5*X (Model is correct)\n",
        "##### H1: μ > 1000 + 5*X (Costs are higher than model prediction)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "TSq7edsYGZhM"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## Step 2: Import Libraries"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "Q-UYmAgvHNbL"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 2,
      "metadata": {
        "id": "7lKkyJDsGE79"
      },
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "import math\n",
        "from scipy.stats import norm"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## Step 3: Given Data"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "t4ypdMEcHnak"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "sample_mean = 3050   # x̄ = sample mean weekly cost\n",
        "n = 25               # sample size\n",
        "X_mean = 600         # mean units produced\n",
        "X_sd = 25            # std. dev. of units produced\n",
        "\n",
        "# Theoretical mean weekly cost from model\n",
        "theoretical_mean = 1000 + 5 * X_mean\n",
        "theoretical_mean"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "lEZusYp_HeZE",
        "outputId": "3618e249-bc5e-4ea3-80ee-75d615302395"
      },
      "execution_count": 4,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "execute_result",
          "data": {
            "text/plain": [
              "4000"
            ]
          },
          "metadata": {},
          "execution_count": 4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## Step 4: Calculate Sigma & Standard Error"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "eT0RAtUWH3Py"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "sigma = 5 * X_sd                   # Standard deviation of weekly costs\n",
        "se = sigma / math.sqrt(n)          # Standard error of mean\n",
        "\n",
        "sigma, se"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "XnmVgpKfHzip",
        "outputId": "1208e586-a233-4bee-b438-936102448659"
      },
      "execution_count": 5,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "execute_result",
          "data": {
            "text/plain": [
              "(125, 25.0)"
            ]
          },
          "metadata": {},
          "execution_count": 5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## Step 5: Test Statistic"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "s-OnokMCIeYo"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "z = (sample_mean - theoretical_mean) / se\n",
        "z"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "xlca-LbKIZ8p",
        "outputId": "3fa06b8e-e733-402a-fd80-7cc665e8e86b"
      },
      "execution_count": 6,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "execute_result",
          "data": {
            "text/plain": [
              "-38.0"
            ]
          },
          "metadata": {},
          "execution_count": 6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## Step 6: Critical Value"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "9XPopGH1Im67"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "alpha = 0.05\n",
        "z_critical = norm.ppf(1 - alpha)   # One-tailed test\n",
        "z_critical"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "wrnC_4dwIjcY",
        "outputId": "71421330-a80c-477f-b829-ed20e8edbe49"
      },
      "execution_count": 7,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "execute_result",
          "data": {
            "text/plain": [
              "np.float64(1.6448536269514722)"
            ]
          },
          "metadata": {},
          "execution_count": 7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## Step 7: Decision"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "65drWoEkIvou"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "if z > z_critical:\n",
        "    decision = \"Reject H0\"\n",
        "else:\n",
        "    decision = \"Fail to Reject H0\"\n",
        "\n",
        "decision"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/",
          "height": 35
